{
  "stem": "27509.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The occasion for me to go to the ghetto was other formal one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It came about as a result of the Japanese [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] intent of sending all British citizens into camp for the duration of the war, because they were-- they were enemy s-- subjects, being British, and they had to be interned, the same as the Japanese were interned in America.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that included the [INAUDIBLE] and everybody else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It so happened that [INAUDIBLE] from the charitable trust funds built a Jewish day school in [INAUDIBLE] where the German Jews live prior to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For that purpose to give Jewish children some form of Jewish education.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when they were due to leave and go to the-- to camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To-- not to the ghetto, to camp, to Japanese camp, not the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were British citizens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not stateless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then they wanted to hand over this school to some authority because they won't be there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who will run it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they turned to the Russian Jewish community to take over the responsibility for that school for the duration, because the Russian Jews were not subject to going to internment because were Russian and stateless, and were not enemy subjects.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they were left unmolested.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were left [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Russian Jews said yes, they will do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they made a time to go and have a look at the entire place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But there was one little hitch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Russian Jews knew about Jewish day schools less than I know what's happening on Mars today.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
